    <item>
      <title>国际原子能机构称伊朗需要与特朗普达成核谅解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/iran-needs-to-strike-nuclear-understanding-with-trump-iaea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界最高核监管机构表示，伊朗需要与唐纳德·特朗普政府就其核活动达成谅解，以避免被卷入中东的另一场军事冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/iran-needs-to-strike-nuclear-understanding-with-trump-iaea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:45:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦称每次会议都采取行动是可行的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/ecb-s-villeroy-says-it-s-plausible-to-act-at-each-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行有可能在每次即将召开的会议上降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/ecb-s-villeroy-says-it-s-plausible-to-act-at-each-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:42:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国发行 2040 年债券，寻求在初步协议成功的基础上再接再厉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-offers-2040-bonds-seeking-to-build-on-success-of-initial-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将于周二通过银行发售 2040 年到期的债券，希望借此巩固此前发售的成功以及本月早些时候遭遇抛售后需求的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-offers-2040-bonds-seeking-to-build-on-success-of-initial-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国自五月以来首次通过银行发售债券，被抢购一空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/france-offers-bonds-via-banks-for-first-time-in-eight-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国新政府试图获得足够的支持来通过急需的预算，该国约八个月以来首次银团债券发售获得了大量投资者的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/france-offers-bonds-via-banks-for-first-time-in-eight-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通“作战室”审视特朗普总统任期的最初几天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/jpmorgan-war-room-is-examining-first-days-of-trump-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产和财富管理部门主管玛丽·埃尔多斯表示，摩根大通已经派遣团队加班加点地分析特朗普总统任期内政策转变的早期轮廓所带来的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/jpmorgan-war-room-is-examining-first-days-of-trump-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 08:52:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯警告投资者不会相信未来的支出削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/reeves-warned-investors-won-t-believe-in-future-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 宣布进一步推迟支出限制，她将很难让金融城相信她的财政信誉，因为她已经试图将有政治争议的决定推迟到工党议会任期的结束阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/reeves-warned-investors-won-t-believe-in-future-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新世界银行承诺提供 150 亿美元贷款，利润率受限，压力加大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/new-world-offers-15-billion-for-loan-collateral-as-stress-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着香港房地产开发商新世界发展有限公司将其部分最有价值的资产抵押以获得贷款，且券商不再为该公司的股票和债券提供融资，该公司信贷压力的迹象正在加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/new-world-offers-15-billion-for-loan-collateral-as-stress-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 02:21:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暂停加征关税缓解通胀担忧 美国债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/treasuries-rally-on-first-trading-day-under-trump-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统暂时没有对中国征收特定关税，因市场对唐纳德·特朗普政策将加剧通胀的担忧有所缓解，美国国债价格出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/treasuries-rally-on-first-trading-day-under-trump-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普继续威胁征收关税，大宗商品价格回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普重申了对墨西哥和加拿大征收关税的计划，尽管他没有承诺对中国征收关税，但此举再次引发了贸易战的担忧，导致石油和基本金属价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 23:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
